Title: Parrot Anafi Drone Reverse Engineering | HardBreak
Description: In this example, we demonstrate how we reverse-engineered the communication between the Parrot Anafi consumer drone and its controller, which connect via Wi-Fi. The Parrot Anafi hosts its own Wi-Fi network, allowing either the controller or a phone running the Freeflight app to connect. Our goal was to understand the signals sent to the Anafi for initiating takeoff and landing sequences.

Title: requirements.txt
Description:
so my roommate (@aadillpickle) made this really cool site to acknowledge the people in his life who have helped him become the person he is today.
it’s kinda like a python requirements.txt file, but for humans (or a javascript package.json file for you web nerds out there).
instead of listing software dependencies, it lists people dependencies.
people that have helped shape who you are today, each with their own unique qualities that you’ve learned from.
